<p>Kim teamed the look with high-waisted denim ripped jeans and a white clutch bag.</p>

<p>The television personality was joined by husband Kroy Biermann, 35, and her daughter Brielle, 23.   </p>

<p>Also joining the families for dinner was Sylvester's model daughter Sistine, 22. </p>

